## Doc Consistency
- Docs must reflect the real add-on configuration.
  - **Source of truth** for add-on options: `moltbot_gateway/config.json`.
- If behavior/options/defaults change, always update the affected docs.

## Examples & Safety
- Never include real keys/tokens/passwords in examples.
  - Use placeholders like `sk-ant-...`, `YOUR-HA-IP`, `YOUR-BOT-TOKEN`.
- Prefer clear, short examples (copy/paste friendly).
